THE GAME
--------

  'Vetex' is a Workbench game where you have to move two 'X'
shapes, so they are placed on the same tile. You have to click
on these shapes, as well as on small coloured squares that are
located on tiles that are linked to the empty tile... When both
'X' shapes are on the same tile, the 'X' shapes explode and the
game board is completed...

  You can restart a game board, by clicking on the 'Replay'
button, but be aware that the amount of moves you make for the
current game board is added up until you complete it...

  Complete each game board in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

